item.title: CVE-2023-0689|2024-09-27T14:23:45.226Z -- xpeedstudio -- metform%20elementor%20contact%20form%20builder
item.description: The Metform Elementor Contact Form Builder for WordPress is vulnerable to Information Disclosure via the 'mf_first_name' shortcode in versions up to, and including, 3.3.1. This allows authenticated attackers, with subscriber-level capabilities or above to obtain sensitive information about arbitrary form submissions, including the submitter's first name.
